        <h2>It's Not Just in Your Wallet, It's in Your Heart</h2>
        <p>Your passion for the sport and your loyalty to the Red Devils now comes with a host of rewards, benefits, and privileges with the only football-loving Credit Card in the UAE.</p>
        
        <h3>Rewards and Benefits</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Access to over 25 regional and international lounges.</li>
            <li>Bon Appétit - an exclusive dining experience.</li>
            <li>Earn 10X RED Points on sports goods, 5X RED Points on dining spends, and 2X on all international spends.</li>
            <li>Activate your card and spend AED 2,000 within the first 30 days to receive a Manchester United Home Jersey.</li>
